": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "MakeItStable_MR_Screenshot_01.png", "id": "794000795994274", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr6-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982683_794000799327607_7875931496887846762_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=wtNlFFYuXzEQ7kNvgFS26gv&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr6-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCqd7OPCtbU8K4zL3hg92segu4uK7G6JjgAnbt0nAG7pw&oe=671650C7"}, {"file_name": "MakeItStable_MR_Screenshot_02.png", "id": "1942884959505069", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr8-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75203618_1942884962838402_4391026615187653081_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=q8RBxVhgO3QQ7kNvgGTVjvb&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBeCjfGPYSKgELvXlo1fmn1Wdg-VmKkoVS1CcJeo9XwVQ&oe=671633DC"}, {"file_name": "MakeItStable_MR_Screenshot_03.png", "id": "1512509456322226", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr8-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75272211_1512509459655559_390244531742034050_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=gilCAR6p5icQ7kNvgGHqkGu&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAmuDk1gKLg1kZyg2r2hjP31KTyMchoz_W9DzsI3s5pJQ&oe=67163F69"}, {"file_name": "MakeItStable_MR_Screenshot_04.png", "id": "876157110541473", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr8-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982710_876157113874806_7180484558048733222_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=O9f2TukhxnkQ7kNvgEYpvhm&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCfmPLVglKm5pFrO24NQLGSP-Xc65SHiuOlpB8YUEA0_A&oe=671622AD"}, {"file_name": "MakeItStable_MR_Screenshot_05.png", "id": "505699135518169", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr8-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035404_505699138851502_1444690351639329884_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=LGT28Mt2ye8Q7kNvgHRuQqu&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBHkO1wJH2N0SHRpZpsgR39tOtHLHubakw5SMFOeZBdDw&oe=67163BE2"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "MakeItStable_Cover_Trailer.png", "id": "510078601666909", "uri": "https://scontent-lhr6-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974827_510078605000242_5105214940117197736_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_aid=0&_nc_ohc=_8gWj9H9vQMQ7kNvgHEvy25&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lhr6-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBLd30DrkDSPAAwXhJqpMspOWYKnX0kUW8D8xH1ekqppg&oe=6716371B"}, "display_name": "Make It Stable", "keywords": ["casual", "fun", "stack", "tower", "building"], "long_description": "In Make It Stable your mission is simple yet exhilarating: balance the tallest tower using a variety of objects. But beware, each level is a unique challenge special mechanics!\n\nDownload Make It Stable now for free to dive into the Daily Challenge and enjoy a taste of the Campaign Mode. Your tower-building adventure awaits! \n\n\ud83e\udd47**Join the Daily Challenges!**\n\n- Compete with players worldwide to stack the highest tower!\n- Face new objects and unique events daily, from themed days to light-out modes.\n\n\ud83e\udde9**Enjoy the Campaign Mode (In-App Purchase,)**\n\n- 40 levels across 4 worlds with different materials and mechanics to stack!\n- No attempts, no pressure.\n- Access previous Daily Challenges for fun!\n\n\ud83e\udde8**Unique Mechanics and Engaging Objects**\n\n- Engage with lifelike physics and interactive, weldable, and repellent parts that make every game a unique experience.\n- Enjoy stacking fun and reactive objects with the cutest of faces!\n\n\ud83c\udf89**Fun and Challenging**\n\n- Simple yet challenging, Make It Stable offers fun and excitement as it easy to play and hard to master.\n- Playable with controllers or hand-tracking\n\nWhether you want to enjoy the leisurely pace of Campaign Mode or the competitive thrill of the Daily Challenge, every game promises to test your patience and creativity with endless fun. \n\n**How high can you go?** It's time to find out!", "short_description": "Get your stacking skills ready with Make It Stable, a thrilling single player, physics-based mixed reality game. With over 100 different objects, each with its own personality, and four unique, mechanic-based worlds, Make It Stable is as fun as it is challenging!\n\nReady to reach new heights? \n\nDownload Make It Stable now for free and compete on the Daily Challenge. Dive into the initial levels of the Campaign Mode and discover all the different materials and combinations!\n"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "505451408747655", "locale": "es_ES", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Make It Stable", "keywords": ["torre", "equilibrio", "ni\u00f1os", "divertido"], "long_description": "En Make It Stable tu misi\u00f3n es simple pero desafiante: equilibrar la torre m\u00e1s alta utilizando una variedad de objetos. Pero cuidado, \u00a1cada nivel es un desaf\u00edo \u00fanico de mec\u00e1nica especial!\n\nDescarga ahora Make It Stable gratis para competir en el Desaf\u00edo Diario y disfrutar de una muestra del Modo Campa\u00f1a. \n\n**\ud83e\udd47\u00danete a los Desaf\u00edos Diarios**\n\n- \u00a1Compite con jugadores de todo el mundo para apilar la torre m\u00e1s alta!\n- Enfr\u00e9ntate a nuevos objetos y eventos \u00fanicos a diario, desde d\u00edas tem\u00e1ticos hasta un modos de \u201cluces fuera\u201d.\n\n\ud83e\udde9**Disfruta del modo Campa\u00f1a (compra desde la aplicaci\u00f3n)**\n\n- \u00a140 niveles en 4 mundos con diferentes materiales y mec\u00e1nicas para apilar!\n- Sin intentos, sin presi\u00f3n.\n- Accede a desaf\u00edos diarios anteriores aleatorios por pura diversi\u00f3n\n\n\ud83e\udde8**Mec\u00e1nicas \u00fanicas y objetos interactivos**.\n\n- Juega con f\u00edsicas realistas y piezas interactivas, soldables y repelentes que hacen de cada partida una experiencia \u00fanica.\n- Disfruta apilando objetos divertidos y reactivos con las caras de lo m\u00e1s expresivas.\n\n\ud83c\udf89**Diversi\u00f3n para todos**\n\n- Sencillo pero desafiante, Make It Stable es perfecto para jugadores de todas las edades.\n- Se puede jugar con mandos o con seguimiento de manos.\n\nTanto si quieres disfrutar del ritmo pausado del Modo Campa\u00f1a como de la emoci\u00f3n competitiva del Desaf\u00edo Diario, cada partida promete poner a prueba tu paciencia y creatividad con una diversi\u00f3n sin fin.\n\n**\u00bfQu\u00e9 tan alto puedes llegar?** \u00a1Es hora de averiguarlo!", "short_description": "Prepara tus habilidades de equilibrio con Make It Stable, un emocionante juego de realidad mixta basado en f\u00edsicas para un solo jugador. Con m\u00e1s de 100 objetos diferentes, cada uno con su propia personalidad, y cuatro mundos \u00fanicos basados en mec\u00e1nicas, Make It Stable es tan divertido como desafiante.\n\n\nDescarga ahora Make It Stable gratis y compite en el Desaf\u00edo Diario. Tambi\u00e9n puedes sumergirte en los niveles iniciales del Modo Campa\u00f1a y descubrir todos los materiales y combinaciones."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://makeitstablexr.com/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Odders Lab", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://odderslab.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "394813081514456"}, {"id": "377978390272490"}, {"id": "275629210202852"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "es"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "26587982204178509"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "26582974227983976"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "26582974227983976"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1728979200, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "26582974227983976"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "27198615489781841", "version": "1.0.7"}, "id": "522543093471753", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "26313534838289915", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "27198615489781841"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "522543093471753"}]}, "change_log": "MAKE IT STABLE - 1.0.7  - October 2024\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nThank you for all the love and enthusiasm you're showing forMake It Stable! \ud83d\ude80 As always, we're committed to improving it every week to make the experience even more amazing. Here's what's new in this update:\n\n\u2728 Bug fixes: We've squashed some bugs that were lurking around. Everything should run much smoother now!\n\n\u26a1 Performance optimization: We've fine-tuned the game so it runs even better on both Meta Quest 2 and Meta Quest 3.\n\n\ud83c\udfa8 Visual improvements: Some objects got a little makeover and now look better than ever!\n\nKeep building those epic towers and sharing your adventures with us. This is just the beginning! \ud83d\udd25\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n\u00a1Gracias por todo el cari\u00f1o y el entusiasmo que est\u00e1is mostrando por el juego! \ud83d\ude80 Como siempre, estamos comprometidos a mejorarlo cada semana para que la experiencia sea cada vez m\u00e1s incre\u00edble. Aqu\u00ed ten\u00e9is las novedades de esta actualizaci\u00f3n:\n\n\u2728 Correcci\u00f3n de errores: hemos eliminado algunos bugs de nuestra torre de objetos. \u00a1Tu experiencia deber\u00eda ser mucho mejor!\n\n\u26a1 Optimizaci\u00f3n de rendimiento: ajustes para que tanto en Meta Quest 2 como en Meta Quest 3, el juego sea a\u00fan m\u00e1s fluido.\n\n\ud83c\udfa8 Mejoras visuales: algunos objetos han recibido un peque\u00f1o lavado de cara, \u00a1ahora lucen m\u00e1s espectaculares que nunca!\n\nSeguid construyendo esas torres \u00e9picas y compartiendo vuestras aventuras con nosotros. \u00a1Esto solo es el principio! \ud83d\udd25\n\n", "created_date": 1729080936, "id": "27198615489781841", "version": "1.0.7", "version_code": 100070001, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "26313534838289915", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "27198615489781841"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1729072277, "id": "27197425783234145", "version": "1.0.6", "version_code": 100060001, "release_status": "PENDING", "status": "DRAFT", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "26313534838289915", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "27198615489781841"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 17290685